metadata.name: / Whale Shark ED : 1
metadata.description:
Found myself face to face with one of the biggest sea creatures on earth and the least I could say is, it was magical...   

These creatures effortlessly glide around - pretty much like water golden retrievers, so happy and interactive.

Thankfully we were there to save one from a fisherman's net - and now there's one more alive thanks to this photo!
